third-party libraries needed to compile:
./3rd/glew-1.10.0
./3rd/freeglut-2.8.1
./3rd/glm
./audiere-1.9.4-win32

key controls:

F1 - draw FPS
F8 - draw edges
F9 - enable debug mode
F12 - draw debug info
ESC - exit game

v - draw HUD
m - capture mouse
n - minimalize/maximalize
k - draw collision edges


